title: Back From Thanksgiving! + Sam Hunt Performs Bluegrass Versions of His Songs + Eddie Agrees To Sell His Soul To Bobby…We Talk to A Lawyer About Legalities!!
itunes:title: Back From Thanksgiving! + Sam Hunt Performs Bluegrass Versions of His Songs + Eddie Agrees To Sell His Soul To Bobby…We Talk to A Lawyer About Legalities!!
description:
We’re back from Thanksgiving! We share how we spent our holiday. Sam Hunt stops by the studio with a bluegrass band and performs some of his hits! Eddie agrees to sell his soul to Bobby. We talk to John Morgan of Morgan & Morgan to hear about the legal ramifications of the deal.
